body:
I came across `DataFormats/TrackingSeed` package while searching for something else. According to git history the last non-technical-migration commit appears to be from 2006, and the package is not used by anybody, i.e. it looks like a (very) old remnant. This PR removes the package.

Tested in 8_1_0_pre9, no changes expected in monitored quantities.

@rovere @VinInn
